        <p>What if the 3rd partysite is not carrying the capability? The site either passes a DOM
            element as the container for the <codeph>&lt;iframe></codeph> or, if not supplied, a FAB
            is created which, upon clicking, renders the <codeph>&lt;iframe></codeph> in it. The
            <codeph>&lt;iframe></codeph> contains the issuer's site's <term>iframe-outlet</term>
            page, which shows a <b>list</b> of tokens (by itemView). </p>
